                <text type="forecast_winds">Northwesterly 15 to 20 knots, reaching up to 25 knots south of Port Vincent to Brighton early in the morning. Winds turning west to southwesterly below 10 knots during the morning.</text>
                <text type="forecast_seas">1 to 2 metres, decreasing below 1 metre around midday.</text>
